## function __copy\_sketchpad__\(name\)

Returns a copy of a `sketchpad`'s canvas.

__Arguments:__

- `name` -- The name of the `sketchpad`.
	- Type: str, unicode

__Returns:__

A copy of the `sketchpad`'s canvas.

- Type: canvas

</div>

