<div class="FunctionDoc YAMLDoc" id="flush_log" markdown="1">

## function __flush\_log__\(\)

Forces any pending write operations to the log file to be written to disk.

__Example:__

{% highlight python %}
log('TRIAL FINISHED')
flush_log()
{% endhighlight %}

</div>

[flush_log]: #flush_log

